title: Nuclear structure of 229,231Th studied with the 230,232Th(d,t) reactions

x4freetext: Nuclear structure of 229,231Th studied with the
230,232Th(d,t) reactions

x4codes.hlp: United States of America, United States of America

x4freetext: Dartmouth College,Hanover,New Hampshire,USA

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Nuclear Physics, Section A, Vol.809, p.129 (2008)

x4freetext: Experiments were performed using beams
of 17 MeV deuterons from the McMaster University
Tandem Van de Graaff accelerator
Reaction products were analysed with an
Enge split-pole magnetic spectrograph and detected
with photographic plates.
E-EXC excitation energies are measured relative
to 554.6 keV and 29.2 keV levels for 231Th and 229Th,
respectively.
